Detailed Description

em>CphsServPflProvider is the provider to retrieve data relating to the Customer service profile from the sim (CPHS4_2.WW6 B4.7). An instance of this class is part of the the Apoxi Data Control. A pointer to this provider can be retrieved from the main provider via the id:

c_cphs_costumer_prof_provider_id

Following column ids are defined:

all columns represents a BOOLEAN value and shall be casted to BOOLEAN

c_serv_cfu_id :NumberType: c_serv_cfb_id :NumberType: c_serv_cfnry_id :NumberType: c_serv_cfnrc_id :NumberType: c_serv_ct_id :NumberType:

c_serv_boac_id :NumberType: c_serv_boic_id :NumberType: c_serv_boic_exhc_id :NumberType: c_serv_baic_id :NumberType: c_serv_bic_roam_id :NumberType:

c_serv_mpty_id :NumberType: c_serv_cug_id :NumberType: c_serv_aoc_id :NumberType: c_serv_pref_cug_id :NumberType: c_serv_cug_oa_id :NumberType:

c_serv_hold_id :NumberType: c_serv_cw_id :NumberType: c_serv_ccbs_id :NumberType: c_serv_usr_usr_sig_id :NumberType:

c_serv_sm_mt_id :NumberType: c_serv_sm_mo_id :NumberType: c_serv_sm_cb_id :NumberType: c_serv_repl_path_id :NumberType: c_serv_del_conf_id :NumberType: c_serv_protid_id :NumberType: c_serv_val_per_id :NumberType:

c_serv_als_id :NumberType:

c_serv_clip_id :NumberType: c_serv_co_lr_id :NumberType: c_serv_co_lp_id :NumberType: c_serv_mci_id :NumberType: c_serv_cli_send_id :NumberType: c_serv_cli_block_id :NumberType:

c_serv_gprs_id :NumberType: c_serv_hscsd_id :NumberType: c_serv_vgrp_call_id :NumberType: c_serv_voice_bcst_serv_id :NumberType: c_serv_mtpl_subs_pfl_id :NumberType: c_serv_mtpl_band_id :NumberType:

c_serv_plmn_mode_id :NumberType: c_serv_vps_id :NumberType: c_serv_smmo_paging_id :NumberType: c_serv_smmo_email_id :NumberType: c_serv_fax_id :NumberType: c_serv_data_id :NumberType: c_serv_language_id :NumberType:

This provider only consists of one fixed row.

NOTE: Please do not instantiate this class.
